<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 18:18:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>北约秘书长警告俄罗斯与中国、伊朗和朝鲜的关系构成威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-chief-warns-threat-russian-ties-with-china-iran-north-korea-2024-11-12/</link><description>北约秘书长马克·吕特周二表示，俄罗斯与中国、朝鲜和伊朗日益增长的经济和军事合作正在威胁欧洲、印太地区和北美。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 15:12:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-chief-warns-threat-russian-ties-with-china-iran-north-korea-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康：在与政府谈判期间正在审查在英国的4.5亿英镑投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-450-million-pound-investment-uk-under-review-amid-talks-with-govt-2024-11-12/</link><description>伦敦上市制药商阿斯利康表示，其 3 月份宣布的在英国投资 4.5 亿英镑（5.767 亿美元）用于疫苗研发的计划正在接受审查，同时与政府就激励措施进行谈判仍在继续。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 14:32:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-450-million-pound-investment-uk-under-review-amid-talks-with-govt-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>沙特队期待雷纳德重拾昔日辉煌，重燃世界杯挑战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/saudis-look-renard-recapture-past-glories-reignite-world-cup-challenge-2024-11-12/</link><description>周四，沙特阿拉伯将在墨尔本举行的亚洲世界杯预选赛中迎战澳大利亚队，希望重燃昔日的辉煌，绿猎鹰队的目标是随着埃尔维·雷纳德的回归，摆脱罗伯托·曼奇尼时代的低迷状态。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 14:23:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/saudis-look-renard-recapture-past-glories-reignite-world-cup-challenge-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>盈利和中国担忧拖累富时 100 指数跌至 3 个月低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/earnings-china-worries-drag-ftse-100-three-month-low-2024-11-12/</link><description>周二，伦敦基准指数触及三个多月来的最低点，原因是担心美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普可能任命一名对华鹰派为主要外交官，以及一些令人失望的企业最新消息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 13:35:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/earnings-china-worries-drag-ftse-100-three-month-low-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康称被拘留的中国区负责人有律师，但公司仍处于黑暗之中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-ceo-says-detained-china-chief-has-lawyer-we-have-no-information-2024-11-12/</link><description>阿斯利康首席执行官周二表示，上个月被中国当局拘留的阿斯利康中国区总裁王立峰正在与律师联系，但该公司对此案的信息很少。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 13:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-ceo-says-detained-china-chief-has-lawyer-we-have-no-information-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>伊拉克入围 11 家公司参与 Grand Faw 港口运营，将于 2025 年 1 月做出决定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iraq-shortlists-11-firms-grand-faw-port-operation-decision-january-2025-2024-11-12/</link><description>伊拉克港口总公司总经理周二对路透表示，伊拉克已入围 11 家航运公司竞逐 Grand Faw 港口运营合同，预计将于 2025 年 1 月决定获胜者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iraq-shortlists-11-firms-grand-faw-port-operation-decision-january-2025-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国的不安和盈利拖累欧洲斯托克600指数跌至三个月低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/european-shares-under-pressure-china-worries-downbeat-earnings-2024-11-12/</link><description>欧洲主要股指周二暴跌 2%，跌至近三个月低点，因对中美关系命运的担忧给对世界第二大经济体有重大影响的股票蒙上阴影，同时一些悲观的盈利也承压。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:44:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/european-shares-under-pressure-china-worries-downbeat-earnings-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国珠海发生肇事逃逸事件 35人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/thirty-five-people-killed-hit-and-run-incident-zhuhai-china-2024-11-12/</link><description>据国家电视台中央电视台周二报道，周一晚间，一辆汽车在中国南部城市珠海的一个体育中心外冲撞一群人，造成 35 人死亡、43 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:02:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/thirty-five-people-killed-hit-and-run-incident-zhuhai-china-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：比特币：达到 90,000 美元及以上？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-11-12/</link><description>达拉·拉纳辛格 (Dhara Ranasinghe) 展望美国和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:02:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>世贸组织可能会在特朗普就任总统之前寻求重新任命主席</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/wto-hold-special-meeting-end-nov-weigh-chiefs-reappointment-2024-11-12/</link><description>周二的一份文件显示，世界贸易组织计划在本月晚些时候召开最高决策机构特别会议，会上可能会重新任命总干事恩戈齐·奥孔乔-伊韦阿拉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 09:54:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/wto-hold-special-meeting-end-nov-weigh-chiefs-reappointment-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>珠海航展开幕，中国商飞订单及未来航天飞机一睹风采</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/zhuhai-air-show-opens-with-orders-comac-glimpse-future-spaceplane-2024-11-12/</link><description>中国的航空航天雄心在第一天成为焦点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 09:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/zhuhai-air-show-opens-with-orders-comac-glimpse-future-spaceplane-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，北京推动加入保障巴基斯坦公民安全的努力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/beijing-pushes-join-security-efforts-citizens-pakistan-sources-say-2024-11-12/</link><description>消息人士称，在卡拉奇发生被视为重大安全漏洞的汽车爆炸事件后，北京在会谈中敦促巴基斯坦允许本国安全人员为在这个南亚国家工作的数千名中国公民提供保护。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 09:18:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/beijing-pushes-join-security-efforts-citizens-pakistan-sources-say-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国航空工业集团公司在珠海航展上展示无人货运飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-avic-reveals-uncrewed-cargo-spaceplane-zhuhai-air-show-2024-11-12/</link><description>国有航天公司中航工业周二在中国最大的珠海航展上推出了中国第一架商用无人驾驶航天飞机，其任务是为中国空间站提供补给。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 08:42:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-avic-reveals-uncrewed-cargo-spaceplane-zhuhai-air-show-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>联合国秘书长警告COP29峰会，否则人类将面临气候灾难</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/cop29-pay-up-or-face-climate-led-disaster-humanity-warns-un-chief-2024-11-12/</link><description>联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯周二在 COP29 峰会上告诉世界各国领导人“付出代价”以防止气候引发的人道主义灾难，并表示限制全球气温破坏性上升的时间已经不多了。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 08:20:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/cop29-pay-up-or-face-climate-led-disaster-humanity-warns-un-chief-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国正在推动其放弃南海主权主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-its-under-pressure-china-cede-claims-south-china-sea-2024-11-12/</link><description>马尼拉国防部长吉尔伯托·特奥多罗周二在堪培拉会见澳大利亚国防部长后表示，中国正在加大对菲律宾的压力，要求其承认其在南海的主权。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 06:56:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-its-under-pressure-china-cede-claims-south-china-sea-2024-11-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>